            , was indicted for <rs id="t18000528-84-off483" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000528-84-off483" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000528-84-off483" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000528-84-cd484" type="crimeDate">24th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-84-off483 t18000528-84-cd484"></join>, two muslin handkerchiefs, value 2s. a linen handkerchief, value 6d. two petticoats, value 4s. and a muslin gown, value 3s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000528-84-victim866" type="victimName">
                     Elias 
                     Creed
                  <interp inst="t18000528-84-victim866" type="surname" value="Creed"></interp>
